headline: Texas Pacific Land, A Steady Eddie Stock, Clears Benchmark; Prepping For A Run Higher?
summary: Shares of pure play land and resource management company Texas Pacific Land grew steadily for years.  The No. 1 ranked company in its industry, Texas Pacific operates in the resource-rich Permian Basin.  It more than doubled in the last 16 months and traded around 1,128 Tuesday afternoon.
